    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/42ca63ae952453af6343cb0ab3ad52e0.avif?t=1711694877\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/5619ff03ae1e4b951dde99a20c7d6ef9.avif?t=1711694877\" width=616 height=164 /></span><br>游戏为开放世界，含有丰富的可探索内容，你将经历独特的旅程，发现新的物灵，与其成为好友，获取新的情报。击败新的敌人，获得特殊的材料，打造专属装备。前往新的地点，完成光荣的使命，成为他人的依靠。<br>NPC对话含有不同的选择，会导致事情往不同的方向发展。游戏内的昼夜系统，也会使你在不同时间，体验到不同的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/90a8e2b86db35a9e5c42f6ed7984b131.poster.avif?t=1711694877\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/90a8e2b86db35a9e5c42f6ed7984b131.webm?t=1711694877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/90a8e2b86db35a9e5c42f6ed7984b131.mp4?t=1711694877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/b7e5619c9feff2b3b8f416820344b01b.avif?t=1711694877\" width=616 height=164 /></span><br>游戏拥有高度自由的装备系统，每套装备都有独特的优势劣势属性，取得他们，然后打造出你想要的强力角色。你可以牺牲你的防御，获得高额暴击，也可以获得超高闪避，但代价是承受额外的伤害。你想成为哪种角色，完全取决于你自己。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/67f078ecad2446bd08b7aba8a9da4bc0.poster.avif?t=1711694877\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/67f078ecad2446bd08b7aba8a9da4bc0.webm?t=1711694877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/67f078ecad2446bd08b7aba8a9da4bc0.mp4?t=1711694877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/aaf09e09ab3daa321f1fc627b78b5518.avif?t=1711694877\" width=616 height=164 /></span><br>想要击败敌人，需要用到一些策略。游戏战斗拥有增幅和破防两大主要机制。通过积累增幅点，可以在单个回合，爆发出成吨的伤害。而攻击敌人的弱点，则会使他们进入破防状态，在此状态下的敌人，会变得异常脆弱，抓紧机会进行猛攻吧。敌人也会有强大的技能，只有在合适的时机，通过增幅技巧破防他们，才能创造一线生机。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/d62c5f7530d5a0c8a07e78d90da44db9.poster.avif?t=1711694877\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139850/extras/d62c5f7530d5a0c8a07e78d90da44db9.webm?t=1711694877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>如今夏娜大陆正在遭受磨难，在魔物的施虐下，还暗藏着更邪恶的阴谋，勇者啊，出发吧！在众人期待下成为英雄，或在看破真相后成为恶魔。",
